longsought fbi goal easier access to tax records and consumer 
credit data when hunting a foreign agent fbi agents can get bank 
records in secret without having enough evidence for a criminal 
search warrant but they need such a warrant to obtain tax and 
credit data 
inman suggested that a computer list of officials with access to 
top secrets could be used by the irs to tell you if there was any 
significant change either a bankruptcy or a large gain 
inman also said stiffer penalties could be imposed on officials 
who falsify financial disclosure reports 
noting that john walkers wife barbara concealed his spying 
for 16 years before turning him in inman asked do you set up an 
awards system we do with whistle blowers 
the espionage review was planned before state department 
official felix bloch came under suspicion last year but as one 
intelligence community source said like everything else its 
been driven by some frontburner events including the bloch 
affair in which investigators have almost given up hope of filing 
criminal charges 
inman said one of the biggest difficulties in espionage cases is 
proving intent to harm the united states he suggested spies might 
be charged with crimes other than espionage such as theft of 
government property meeting a foreign agent without reporting it 
as bloch allegedly did also could be made a crime he said 
but one executive branch source dubious about the outside 
advisers usefulness said courts accept the delivery of even one 
piece of classified information to a foreign power as proof of 
intent to harm because the government warns employees who see 
secrets about the danger of exposing them 
theyre focusing on several problems that have been solved 
since they left the government this source said our big 
counterintelligence problem is not new legislation but new values 
in society so people wont be so willing to sell out their 
country 
but an intelligence community source said the need to identify a 
specific secret passed the missing element in the bloch 
investigation means you literally have to catch them 
redhanded 
this problem doesnt come up very often the intelligence 
official said when it does it presents a big hurdle 
