trespassing or other nonviolent offenses will help the homeless 
obtain social security numbers and is flexible about an uneven 
work history 
the census bureau also is funding an assessment of the survey in 
five cities by independent researchers the assessment will be used 
to refine any future count of elusive populations said kim 
hopper the primary researcher in new york 
