claude hilton is contingent on kotellos cooperation in the probe 
the conspiracy count says kotellos acquired classified documents 
from a government employee who was not authorized to release them 
getting classified documents from fowler of boeing sharing 
classified documents with other defense contractors and obtaining 
such documents from them and destroying some of the documents in 
his fireplace at home 
