during pinochets rule they say thousands more were illegally 
imprisoned and many of them were tortured 
aylwin appealed on monday for patience saying there will be 
difficulties because of obstacles and binds left behind for us by 
the former regime 
pinochet enacted lastminute laws and decrees trimming aylwins 
