in washington preservationists have a different concern they 
are pushing for legislation intended to give federal protection to 
endangered historic sites somewhat like the protection now given to 
endangered species of wildlife 
it really is remarkable to say that the snail darter enjoys 
more federal protection than the antietam battlefield says j 
