computers made by sun microsystems inc 
the orginal version of 123 was designed for ibm personal 
computers or ibmcompatible pcs it has become the most popular 
spreadsheet program for these desktop machines but industry 
analysts say cambridge massbased lotus needs to expand out of 
this market to keep growing 
spreadsheets display rows and columns of figures or bar graphs 
and are used to represent such things as a companys financial 
results they are among the more popular type of computer programs 
the new versions of 123 for digital computers are the result 
of a joint development and marketing agreement signed by lotus and 
digital in 1988 digital based in maynard mass is the worlds 
secondlargest computer company after ibm 
digital officials said the pact allows them to offer an 
extremely popular software product to their customers while at the 
same time providing a new revenue source 
with the new software groups of digital computer users in 
different offices or even different countries could work jointly on 
the same spreadsheet said gene hodges an executive with company 
the software links computers ranging from desktop workstations 
to mainframes and allows users of 123 on ibmbased personal 
computers to hook up to a digitalbased system 
this lets people work in teams more effectively hodges said 
in an interview 
neither lotus nor digital released sales projections for the new 
software which is lotus first for digital computers the 
companies also would not disclose how they will split the revenue 
lotus also is working on a version of 123 for apple computer 
inc machines the company says 
